meta.title: 9th Meeting
meta.author: Cenedril Aeglos
pages:
ROLL CALL:
Shaman Dro'Baka - Present
Grandmaster Aeglos - Present
High Lord Allorik - Present
Professor Jon - Present
Billy bob - Present
Councilor Bernie - Absent

Motion 1:
Admin controlled holes through bedrock, but they must be lore based, approved by admins, and preferably be within a player city.

Motion seconded.

Votes:
3 Yay
1 Nay
1 Abstain

Motion carried.

Motion 2:
Password protected server. Emplements a lose password protection to reduce number of randoms, creating a semi-public server.

Motion seconded.

Votes:
3 Yay
0 Nay
2 Abstain

Motion carried.

Motion 3:
Gym addition to the meeting room.

Motion seconded.

Votes:
3 Yay
1 Nay
1 Abstain

Motion carried.

Motion 4:
Increase spawn rate of apples from oak trees.

Motion seconded.

Votes:
3 Yay
0 Nay
2 Abstain

Motion carried.

Motion 5:
When a new plugin is brought forth, a link will be provided to all council members.

Motion seconded.

Votes:
3 Yay
0 Nay
2 Abstain

Motion 6:
Implementing a NPC plugin: Citizens 2. Allows creation of citizens by players that are whitelisted. Players are whitelisted by recommendation. If that is proven untrue (recommended player goofs up and proves to be untrustworthy), they will be

blacklisted permenantly. Whitelisted players can only create default NPCs (no abilities) and then players must pay to admins(server/Agni/etc) a certain price to give the NPC an ability, such as blacksmith.

Motion seconded.

Votes:
5 Yay

Votes unanimous, motion carried.

Motion 7:
Armor weight system.

Motion seconded.

Votes:
1 Yay
3 Nay
1 Abstain

Motion carried.

Motion 8:
No new plugins until currently approved plugins have been implemented.

Motion seconded.

Votes:
5 Yay

Vote unanimous, motion carried.
This concludes the 9th meeting of the Elder Council. Meeting adjurned.
